{"tid":1918676,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點吾買put都可去short美股,Call Spread教學","createTime":"2020-03-10T09:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T04:14:20.000Z","uid":349803,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"062c3759e68b9f0c0471bcbc8e3e79e4257a914d","tid":1918676,"uid":349803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"最近可能大家想買美股put,但現在的options iv好高,買左都可能profit吾多,咁可以點買options short股票呢?<br />\n<br />\n其實可以做short call spread,咁點去short call spread?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們拿MSFT做example,現在MSFT 10/3 收市是150.62<br />\n<br />\nlet's assume 我們認為現在MSFT沒可能20/3高過160,咁我們賣左張 20th Mar $160.00 Call contract, 現在張contract 是 4usd premium 咁 4usdx100 = 400 usd.<br />\n<br />\n如果在20/3 MSFT吾高過160咁我們account便會多左400usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,但是sell call options會有unlimited risk,如果MSFT 上返高位180, 咁我們便會 loss (180-160)x100-400usd =1600 usd,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此我們買張165 call option 做hedge,張165 call option cost 2.54. 咁我們的max profit變左(4-2.54)100=146<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 但同時max loss也只會是 (165-160-1.46)x100=354<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npicture 是example,可以看到profit/loss ratio是大約41%:100%,其實只要MSFT上吾返160便net profit 41%錢.<br />\n<br />\n大家可以上這web玩下,另外要認識下知道什麼是option iv,因為iv 高sell option個profit先會多,但要小心iv可以go both ways,iv高便股票波動高,因此要注意<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.optionsprofitcalculator.com/calculator/call-spread.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.optionsprofitcalculator.com%2Fcalculator%2Fcall-spread.html&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSlDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=7d90c216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.optionsprofitcalculator.com/calculator/call-spread.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqokSOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg